# subscription-model

## Tier Structure
- Four subscription levels with distinct capabilities:
  - Starter: Basic vendor assessment features
  - Professional: Full assessment suite
  - Enterprise: Advanced analytics + custom integrations
  - Federal: FedRAMP-compliant version with specialized controls

## Usage Controls & Limits
Per-tier restrictions:
- Vendor assessments: 10/50/Unlimited
- SBOM scans: 10/50/Unlimited per month
- API calls: 1000/10000/Unlimited per month
- User seats: 5/20/Custom
- Export formats: Basic/All/Custom

## Billing Calculations
- Monthly base rate per tier
- Usage-based components:
  - Overage fees for SBOM scans: $5-20/scan
  - Additional assessments: $10-50 each
  - Extra user seats: $20-50/user/month
- Annual discounts: 20% for all tiers

## Feature Access Matrix
Capability gates by tier:
- Basic Assessment Tools: All tiers
- NIST Framework Integration: Professional+
- Custom Framework Builder: Enterprise only
- FedRAMP Controls: Federal tier only
- API Access: Professional+ 

## Usage Tracking
- Real-time monitoring of:
  - Active assessments
  - SBOM scan counts
  - User seat utilization
  - API call volume
- Monthly usage reports
- Proactive limit notifications

